{"type": "article", "id": 17782, "title": "蜂鸟蚊香", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-19T06:30:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000358jRMzcaDHJ1qNn4lT.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款像蜂鸟一样的蚊香源于秘鲁的世界遗产纳斯卡线条，设计者是日本的组合现代美术二等兵，他们将蜂鸟的造型割进透明的塑料面板里，再将绿色的蚊香捏成线条放近面板塑形，由此做成了这款特别的蚊香。产品目前还没有完全实现商品化，不过却是对蚊香设计的参考。<a href=\"http://jpstore.dwango.jp/products/detail.php?product_id=127\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000356x2quOIh9Gg1AslTk.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62931034\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000356anzQpV6Kd14ysYj7.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62931034\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000357eUBGo3NE7TiDQH4p.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70689655\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606000357Qw6FV3O71dIfYBet.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62931034\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}